{"pageProps":{"entry":{"title":"Noms de rue du Raquet, du bon et du moins bon","description":"La commune de Douai a décidé de consulter ses habitant⋅es pour nommer les 4 nouvelles rues du Raquet.","date":"2023-04-24T11:15:00.000Z","draft":false,"categories":["Politique locale"],"tags":["Douai"],"illustration":{"url":"illustrations/voirie-raquet-1.jpg","alt":"Vue aérienne du Raquet"},"id":"noms-de-rue-du-raquet-du-bon-et-du-moins-bon","content":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":1,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Noms de rue du Raquet, du bon et du moins bon","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":3,"offset":2},"end":{"line":1,"column":48,"offset":47}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":48,"offset":47}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"J'ai découvert ce matin la dernière ","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":49},"end":{"line":3,"column":37,"offset":85}}},{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"opération de démocratie participative mis en œuvre par la ville de Douai","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":39,"offset":87},"end":{"line":3,"column":111,"offset":159}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":37,"offset":85},"end":{"line":3,"column":113,"offset":161}}},{"type":"text","value":".","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":113,"offset":161},"end":{"line":3,"column":114,"offset":162}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":49},"end":{"line":3,"column":114,"offset":162}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pour ce nouvel \"éco\"-quartier du Raquet, il me semble que l'idée de consulter les habitant⋅es est bonne, même si, pardonnez le jeu de mot, il y a quelques trous dans la raquette.","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":164},"end":{"line":5,"column":179,"offset":342}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":164},"end":{"line":5,"column":179,"offset":342}}},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"child